BREAST-COMPOSITION: Dense glandular and scattered fibro-glandular breast parenchyma (ACR D)
FINDINGS: Around 1 o'clock position, there is a round, well-circumscribed opacity measuring approximately 8mm. It has a regular margin and shows no evidence of microcalcifications. This finding is suggestive of a benign fibroadenoma. Short term follow-up is recommended to confirm stability.
